  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICareProviderBackend
    This interface outlines the main CP backend features Javadoc is done in Backend
    IPatientBackend
    This interface outlines the main patient backend features Javadoc is done in Backend
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Backend
    This class is a Singleton class which holds, writes, fetches data for the rest of the app.
    ElasticsearchProblemController
    This class is responsible for tasks that communicate with the DB using ES
    ElasticsearchProblemController.AddCPTask
    add a cp to the DB
    ElasticsearchProblemController.AssignPatientToCPTask
    add patient id to list of assigned patients to a given cp id
    ElasticsearchProblemController.CheckIfCPExistsTask
    check if a cp id exists on the db
    ElasticsearchProblemController.CheckIfPatientIDExistsTask
    check if patient id exists on the DB Task
    ElasticsearchProblemController.GetCPPatientsTask
    get all ids of patients assigned to given cp id
    ElasticsearchProblemController.GetPatientTask
    get patient from db with a given patient ID Task
    ElasticsearchProblemController.SetPatientTask
    upload patient to DB Task
    PatientsWrapper
    wrapper for storing list of assigned patients for a CP (makes ES easier)
